   <body>
      <p>You can exclude products or categories from the qualification rows. The Exclude button is enabled after the products or categories are added.</p>
      <p>To exclude a product and category:</p>
      <ol>
         <li>Click Exclude.The Exclude Products page pop-up appears as follows and it is not editable.<fig>
               <image height="250"
                      placement="break"
                      href="../attachments/108500817/108500810.png"/>
            </fig>
         </li>
         <li>Select the categories in the Included Products tab.</li>
         <li>Click Exclude and Save.<p>You cannot view the excluded categories or products in the Category/Products tab but you can view the excluded categories in the Excluded Products tab.</p>
         </li>
      </ol>
   </body>
